            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>When writing SQL in Express, we can utilize parameterized queries to make database access as flexible as possible.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #2",
            "id": 132703,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Parameterized queries are a type of SQL query in which placeholders are used for values, which are passed as parameters.</p><p>They are used to make working with data convenient but also to prevent SQL injection attacks.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3",
            "id": 132718,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>We have a connection to a database that has a users table with values inside.</p><p>We can now create an SQL query to retrieve an entry.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database = \" /><text value=\"require\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;better-sqlite3&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" db = \" /><text value=\"new\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database(\" /><text value=\"&quot;database.db&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"&quot;SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = 'Alice'&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"86\" endIndex=\"94\" /><option startIndex=\"95\" endIndex=\"105\" /><option startIndex=\"106\" endIndex=\"126\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>SELECT *</code>, followed by <code>FROM users</code>, and finally <code>WHERE name = 'Alice'</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy",
            "id": 132733,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Before we can run it, we need to prepare it with <code>db.prepare</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database = \" /><text value=\"require\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;better-sqlite3&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" db = \" /><text value=\"new\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database(\" /><text value=\"&quot;database.db&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"db.prepare(\" /><text value=\"&quot;SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = 'Alice'&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"85\" endIndex=\"87\" /><option startIndex=\"87\" endIndex=\"88\" /><option startIndex=\"88\" endIndex=\"95\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>db</code>, followed by <code>.</code>, and finally <code>prepare</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy - Copy",
            "id": 132734,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>To keep a reference of our query, we save it in a variable.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database = \" /><text value=\"require\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;better-sqlite3&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" db = \" /><text value=\"new\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database(\" /><text value=\"&quot;database.db&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" query = db.prepare(\" /><text value=\"&quot;SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = 'Alice'&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"85\" endIndex=\"90\" /><option startIndex=\"91\" endIndex=\"96\" /><option startIndex=\"97\" endIndex=\"98\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>const</code>, followed by <code>query</code>, and finally <code>=</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy",
            "id": 132732,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Finally, we can run it and log the result.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database = \" /><text value=\"require\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;better-sqlite3&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" db = \" /><text value=\"new\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database(\" /><text value=\"&quot;database.db&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" query = db.prepare(\" /><text value=\"&quot;SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = 'Alice'&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" user = query.get();\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(user);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"168\" endIndex=\"173\" /><option startIndex=\"173\" endIndex=\"179\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"{ id: 378, name: &quot;Alice&quot; }\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>query</code>, followed by <code>.get()</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy - Copy",
            "id": 132735,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>However, a much better approach is to use a parameterized statement with a <code>?</code> that we can later replace with the actual value.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database = \" /><text value=\"require\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;better-sqlite3&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" db = \" /><text value=\"new\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database(\" /><text value=\"&quot;database.db&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" query = db.prepare(\" /><text value=\"&quot;SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = ?&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" user = query.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Alice&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(user);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"131\" endIndex=\"145\" /><option startIndex=\"172\" endIndex=\"179\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"WHERE name = 'Alice'\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"{ id: 378, name: &quot;Alice&quot; }\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>WHERE name = ?</code>, followed by <code>\"Alice\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #8",
            "id": 132737,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>What is the main advantage of using parameterized queries?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">They make queries reusable and prevent SQL injections</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">They allow the use of complexer queries</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">They make queries reusable and prevent SQL injections.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #10",
            "id": 132741,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Complete the query.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database = \" /><text value=\"require\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;better-sqlite3&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" db = \" /><text value=\"new\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database(\" /><text value=\"&quot;database.db&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" query = db.prepare(\" /><text value=\"&quot;SELECT * FROM products WHERE category = ?&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" product = query.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Electronics&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(product);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"134\" endIndex=\"139\" /><option startIndex=\"140\" endIndex=\"148\" /><option startIndex=\"149\" endIndex=\"150\" /><option startIndex=\"151\" endIndex=\"152\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" id: 1, name: &quot;Laptop&quot;, price: 999, category: &quot;Electronics&quot;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>WHERE</code> followed by <code>category</code> and then <code>=</code>, <code>?</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #9",
            "id": 132739,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>What is a parameterized query?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">A query where placeholders are used for values that are provided when the query is executed</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">A query that automatically fetches parameters from the database</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">A query where placeholders are used for values that are provided when the query is executed.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #11",
            "id": 132742,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Complete the parameterized query.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database = \" /><text value=\"require\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;better-sqlite3&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" db = \" /><text value=\"new\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database(\" /><text value=\"&quot;database.db&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" query = db.prepare(\" /><text value=\"&quot;SELECT * FROM orders WHERE customer_id = ?&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" order = query.get(\" /><text value=\"123\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(order);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"181\" endIndex=\"184\" /><option startIndex=\"152\" endIndex=\"153\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" id: 1, name: &quot;MacBook&quot;, price: 1999, category: &quot;Electronics&quot;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>?</code>, followed by <code>123</code>.</p></body></html>"
